author: dlr
msg: On the merge-tracking branch: Initial cut at implementing the
svn_rangelist_intersect() API.
* subversion/libsvn_subr/mergeinfo.c
(rangelist_intersect_or_remove): New fuction factored out of
svn_rangelist_remove(), and parameterized to handle intersection as
well as removal.  Intersection behavior may not be 100% correct yet.
Eliminated local variable "newrange" to compact code.
(svn_rangelist_remove): Delegate to rangelist_intersect_or_remove().
(svn_rangelist_intersect): Delegate to rangelist_intersect_or_remove(),
and move until after that helper function's definition.
